9 Relating to crimes and offenses; to amend Section
10 13A-12-200.2, Code of Alabama 1975, to further provide for the
11 crime of possession with intent to distribute obscene
12 material.
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
14 Section 1. Section 13A-12-200.2, Code of Alabama 1975,
15 is amended to read as follows:
16 "§13A-12-200.2
17 (a)(1) It shall be unlawful for any person to knowingly
18 distribute, possess with intent to distribute, or offer or
19 agree to distribute any obscene material or any device
20 designed or marketed as useful primarily for the stimulation
21 of human genital organs for any thing of pecuniary value.
22 Material not otherwise obscene may be obscene under this
23 section if the distribution of the material, the offer to do
24 so, or the possession with the intent to do so is a commercial
25 exploitation of erotica solely for the sake of prurient
26 appeal.
27 (2) Any person who violates this subsection shall be
28 guilty of a misdemeanor and, upon conviction, shall be
